Generic Sonic Cloudformation Template Producer

To run, execute:

ant -Ddeployment.xml=<sonic deployment xml>

e.g. The following command produces the Cloudformation template,
sonic.xml.template.

ant -Ddeployment.xml=sonic.xml


The stylesheet cf.xsl controls template production based on the deployment xml.

Read the deployment xml for a full description on each template and how to test.
